            <div class="ri-features">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row ">
                        <div class="col-md-12">
                            <h2>Features</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <p>Powerful, Scalable & Demanding taxi/cab booking app with complete features. It is build with powerful infrastructure and based on GPS for route tracking. This can support any number of drivers.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row ri-fealine">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="ri-feabox">
                                <div class="ri-feaimg">
                                    <img src="img/tracking.svg">
                                </div>
                                <div class="ri-featext">
                                    <h3>Realtime GPS Tracking</h3>
                                    <p>Powerful & highly customised Realtime GPS Tracking algorithm using Kalman Filter and Gyro Api's</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="ri-feabox">
                                <div class="ri-feaimg">
                                    <img src="img/splash.svg">
                                </div>
                                <div class="ri-featext">
                                    <h3>Splash Screen</h3>
                                    <p>User & Driver Applications will display splash screen for few secounds and then accompanied by stylish animation</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="ri-feabox">
                                <div class="ri-feaimg">
                                    <img src="img/Verification.svg">
                                </div>
                                <div class="ri-featext">
                                    <h3>Account Verification</h3>
                                    <p>User & Driver app will need to verify their Mobile Number via OTP received in SMS, app will read sms automaticallyn</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row ri-fealine">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="ri-feabox">
                                <div class="ri-feaimg">
                                    <img src="img/login.svg">
                                </div>
                                <div class="ri-featext">
                                    <h3>Login & Registration</h3>
                                    <p>User & Driver can login using email address and password which they choose during signup proccess.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="ri-feabox">
                                <div class="ri-feaimg">
                                    <img src="img/book.svg">
                                </div>
                                <div class="ri-featext">
                                    <h3>Book A Trip</h3>
                                    <p>Rider will enter the Pickup Location & drop location using auto-complete or manually drag & pin them on the Map.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="ri-feabox">
                                <div class="ri-feaimg">
                                    <img src="img/application.svg">
                                </div>
                                <div class="ri-featext">
                                    <h3>Application Slide Menu</h3>
                                    <p>User can access features of the User App & driver can access his Trips Statistics, Manage Vehicles & documents.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row ri-fealine">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="ri-feabox">
                                <div class="ri-feaimg">
                                    <img src="img/driver-get.svg">
                                </div>
                                <div class="ri-featext">
                                    <h3>Driver Get Online</h3>
                                    <p>Driver has to turn on ON-Duty switch on the App to accept the rides ,This is how he is getting online.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="ri-feabox">
                                <div class="ri-feaimg">
                                    <img src="img/rider.svg">
                                </div>
                                <div class="ri-featext">
                                    <h3>Rider</h3>
                                    <p>Once the confirm booking button has been pressed by rider then will show waiting to user until any driver accept.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="ri-feabox">
                                <div class="ri-feaimg">
                                    <img src="img/Driver Copy.svg">
                                </div>
                                <div class="ri-featext">
                                    <h3>Driver</h3>
                                    <p>First Driver in the range of 5 Km's will receive a notification on their mobile using push notification.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row ri-fealine">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="ri-feabox">
                                <div class="ri-feaimg">
                                    <img src="img/invoice.svg">
                                </div>
                                <div class="ri-featext">
                                    <h3>Invoice Summary</h3>
                                    <p>Once driver slide Trip complete button he is redirected to statistics and user will see ride summary on screen.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="ri-feabox">
                                <div class="ri-feaimg">
                                    <img src="img/review.svg">
                                </div>
                                <div class="ri-featext">
                                    <h3>Review & Rating</h3>
                                    <p>Rider can provide feedback for Driver for each Ride. All feedbacks will be shown on driver's Review & Rating</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="ri-feabox">
                                <div class="ri-feaimg">
                                    <img src="img/edit-profile.svg">
                                </div>
                                <div class="ri-featext">
                                    <h3>Edit Profile</h3>
                                    <p>User & Driver both can manage their profile details like Photo, Name, Email Address, Mobile number & Other</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row ri-fealine">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="ri-feabox">
                                <div class="ri-feaimg">
                                    <img src="img/booking-history.svg">
                                </div>
                                <div class="ri-featext">
                                    <h3>Booking History</h3>
                                    <p>Riders & Drivers get a view of their past trip with detail and also route on map and can filter bookings.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="ri-feabox">
                                <div class="ri-feaimg">
                                    <img src="img/driver-app-manage.svg">
                                </div>
                                <div class="ri-featext">
                                    <h3>Driver App Manage</h3>
                                    <p>Driver can also manage details of their vehicles & documents, vehicle listed using number plate & car type</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ri-downsec">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="ridownsecbtn">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
                                <h2>Download My App</h2>
                                <p>Checkout bellow our live demo on google play store and admin panel demo</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row ri-downappline text-center">
                            <div class="col-md-3">
                                <div class="ri-downappbox">
                                    <h3>User App</h3>
                                    <p>Click bellow google play button to check user taxi/cab app on google play store.</p>

                                    <button class="btn btn-primary ri-appbtn" type="submit">Download on<span>App Stores</span></button>

                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-3">
                                <div class="ri-downappbox">
                                    <h3>Driver App</h3>
                                    <p>Click bellow google play button to check user taxi/cab app on google play store.</p>

                                    <button class="btn btn-primary ri-appbtn" type="submit">Download on<span>App Stores</span></button>

                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-3">
                                <div class="ri-downappbox">
                                    <h3>User App</h3>
                                    <p>Click bellow google play button to check user taxi/cab app on google play store.</p>

                                    <button class="btn btn-primary ri-appbtnand" type="submit">Download on<span>App Stores</span></button>

                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-3">
                                <div class="ri-downappbox">
                                    <h3>Driver App</h3>
                                    <p>Click bellow google play button to check user taxi/cab app on google play store.</p>

                                    <button class="btn btn-primary ri-appbtnand" type="submit">Download on<span>App Stores</span></button>

                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ri-formsec">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6 ri-formtext">
                                <h2>Admin Panel</h2>
                                <p>Admin Login</p>
                                <p>User: admin | Pass: demo</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6 ri-formgroup">
                                <form>
                                    <input type="email" class="form-control ri-username" id="inputEmail4" placeholder="Username">
                                    <input type="password" class="form-control ri-password" id="inputPassword4" placeholder="Password">
                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary booknow">Login</button>
                                </form>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ri-slidersec">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-6 ri-slietext">
